    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦幻旋律》是一款令人容易沉迷的节奏游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的操作，动听的歌曲，带给您梦幻般的心流体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.poster.avif?t=1766152333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.webm?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.mp4?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 10首动听的歌曲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含中日韩俄英多国语言。多种风格，不同的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 简单的操作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行游戏只需要2个按键，任何人都可以快速入门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 每首歌曲包含3个难度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松游玩简单模式，在普通模式中进行练习，最后挑战困难难度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 分数排行榜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力获得更高得分，在排行榜上留下你的名字吧！</p>",
